Package: EcoSdmUy
Title: Species Distribution Modeling for Uruguay
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2026-06-22
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Manuel",
           family = "Spinola",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "manuel.spinola@una.ac.cr")
Description: Interactive Shiny application for species distribution modeling
    in Uruguay, using hexagonal H3 spatial grids and CHELSA bioclimatic
    variables. Built on the h3sdm package. Occurrence data from GBIF and
    iNaturalist.
